      <title>香港零售交易商因热门结构性票据损失 16 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hong-kong-traders-lost-1-6-billion-in-4-days-on-leveraged-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港的零售交易员受到打击，15.5亿美元的杠杆衍生品在近期股市暴跌期间化为乌有，加剧了市场波动，凸显了这种受欢迎的结构性产品的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hong-kong-traders-lost-1-6-billion-in-4-days-on-leveraged-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 02:55:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
