    <item>
      <title>随着中国大陆和香港股市反弹延续，亚洲股市上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数亚洲股市在中国内地和香港股市上涨的带动下上涨，因为投资者押注北京方面的最新刺激措施将为中国股市的暴跌提供支撑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其即将结束加息，最后一步将加息至 45%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/turkey-on-cusp-of-ending-rate-hike-saga-with-last-step-up-to-45</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行将于周四召开一次会议，结束其有史以来最长的货币紧缩周期之一，可能会在周四进行最后一次加息，该会议因围绕行长哈菲兹·盖伊·埃尔坎(Hafize Gaye Erkan)的争议而短暂蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/turkey-on-cusp-of-ending-rate-hike-saga-with-last-step-up-to-45</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
